<section class="ftco-consult bg-primary">
    <div class="container-fluid px-md-4">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-2 text-lg-right">
                <h3 class="mb-4 mb-lg-0">Search A Model</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <form class="consult-form" method="get" enctype="multipart/form-data" asp-controller="Search" asp-action="Search">
                    <div class="d-lg-flex align-items-md-end">
                        <div class="form-field">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <div class="select-wrap">
                                    <div class="icon"><span class="ion-ios-arrow-down"></span></div>
                                    <label>Select Country</label>
                                    <select name="Country" id="1" class="form-control">
                                        @*<option value="">Country</option>*@
                                        <option value="Bulgaria">Bulgaria</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="SearchInputModel.Country" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <div class="select-wrap">
                                    <div class="icon"><span class="ion-ios-arrow-down"></span></div>
                                    <label>Select City</label>
                                    <select name="City" id="2" class="form-control">
                                        @*<option value="">City</option>*@
                                        <option value="Sofia">Sofia</option>
                                        <option value="Plovdiv">Plovdiv</option>
                                        <option value="Blagoevgrad">Blagoevgrad</option>
                                        <option value="Burgas">Burgas</option>
                                        <option value="Varna">Varna</option>
                                        <option value="Stara Zagora">Stara Zagora</option>
                                        <option value="Pleven">Pleven</option>
                                        <option value="Pazardzhik">Pazardzhik</option>
                                        <option value="Veliko Tarnovo">Veliko Tarnovo</option>
                                        <option value="Haskovo">Haskovo</option>
                                        <option value="Ruse">Ruse</option>
                                        <option value="Vratsa">Vratsa</option>
                                        <option value="Sliven">Sliven</option>
                                        <option value="Dobrich">Dobrich</option>
                                        <option value="Shumen">Shumen</option>
                                        <option value="Montana">Montana</option>
                                        <option value="Lovech">Lovech</option>
                                        <option value="Kardzhali">Kardzhali</option>
                                        <option value="Kyustendil">Kyustendil</option>
                                        <option value="Yambol">Yambol</option>
                                        <option value="Razgrad">Razgrad</option>
                                        <option value="Pernik">Pernik</option>
                                        <option value="Gabrovo">Gabrovo</option>
                                        <option value="Silistra">Silistra</option>
                                        <option value="Smolyan">Smolyan</option>
                                        <option value="Targovishte">Targovishte</option>
                                        <option value="Vidin">Vidin</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="SearchInputModel.City" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <div class="select-wrap">
                                    <div class="icon"><span class="ion-ios-arrow-down"></span></div>
                                    <label>Select Gender</label>
                                    <select name="Gender" id="3" class="form-control">
                                        @*<option value="">Gender</option>*@
                                        <option value="Female">Female</option>
                                        <option value="Male">Male</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="SearchInputModel.Gender" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                            <!-- <label for="#">Bust</label> -->
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <div class="select-wrap">
                                    <div class="icon"><span class="ion-ios-arrow-down"></span></div>
                                    <label>Select Age From</label>
                                    <select name="Age" id="4" class="form-control">
                                        @*<option value="">Age from</option>*@
                                        @for (int i = 12; i < 75; i++)
                                        {
                                            <option value="@i">@i</option>
                                        }
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="SearchInputModel.Age" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                            <!-- <label for="#">Bust</label> -->
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <div class="select-wrap">
                                    <div class="icon"><span class="ion-ios-arrow-down"></span></div>
                                    <label>To Age</label>
                                    <select name="To" id="4" class="form-control">
                                        @*<option value="">To</option>*@
                                        @for (int i = 13; i < 76; i++)
                                        {
                                            <option value="@i">@i</option>
                                        }
                                    </select>
                                    <span asp-validation-for="SearchInputModel.To" class="text-danger"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-3 mb-lg-0 mr-4">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="submit" value="Search" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-4">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

    <section class="ftco-section ftco-services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
                    <div class="media block-6 services">
                        <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <span class="flaticon-diamond"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="heading">Finding Agency</h3>
                            <p>Agencies, you are given access to a vast array of models ranging from fresh new talent to proven professionals. With our photo sessions we are able to show you previously undiscovered models and present them in a fresh, high quality yet realistic, light. We show our new faces without complicated hair and makeup, which allows you to see the model and all their potential.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
                    <div class="media block-6 services">
                        <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <span class="flaticon-cosmetics"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="heading">Types of Modeling</h3>
                            <p>Whether you are a Aspiring model or Amateur or a professional model, create your model4you profile and photobooks and instantly increase your international exposure. Be seen on a scale that has previously only been realized by a privileged few. This is your chance to get listed with the most in-demand international agencies and to be selected by the best photographers worldwide. The worlds leading players are watching, so let them see you!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
                    <div class="media block-6 services">
                        <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <span class="flaticon-fashion"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="heading">Freelance</h3>
                            <p>If you’re a freelance model, then you’re representing yourself and you are fully responsible for finding and booking your own work. One major advantage of securing your own work is not having to divide your earnings with your agency so you will take home the full amount of the job. Generally speaking though, freelance modelling gigs tend to pay less than fashion and commercial jobs, as clients that hire freelance models generally have a tighter budget.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
                    <div class="media block-6 services">
                        <div class="icon d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <span class="flaticon-loupe"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h3 class="heading">Search Models</h3>
                            <p>Alternatively search through the selection of professional models, view their profile and previous work to see if it is a fit for your agency or up and coming campaigns. We categorise the models and list their vital statistics to help you find exactly what you are looking for fast!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



